    <h1><br>Tribute to Dr. APJ Abdul Kalam</h1>
    <p class="bio">
        Dr. APJ Abdul Kalam was an Indian scientist and the 11th President of India. He was known for his work in the field of missile technology and his visionary leadership. A humble man with a heart full of dreams, he inspired millions through his passion for education, science, and nation-building. His contributions to India's defense and his commitment to empowering youth remain unparalleled.
    </p>

